瘓成個社會先<br />\n如果唔係你就揸起把菜刀 去達到真攬炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34c0e7804d00fc4f95af84446f5b0e067dae121","tid":1683400,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"推到搞為止"},{"pid":"1874e83a2162521d1eba78525c62738405cb8b4c","tid":1683400,"uid":296650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:49:40.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post有同感嘅各位都請喺其他渠道(Fb Tg twitter)去提倡罷工行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f77b36a72bb4883701c848ff2758d7cf05684f","tid":1683400,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:12:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc655bfed148c291bda3a5fbba9ba51e5adee487","tid":1683400,"uid":219736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:15:33.000Z","msg":"最好時機其實係咁緊急之後嗰日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公務員金融界帶頭最有用<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人唔可以慣</span>"},{"pid":"1cd5a84a0d5f30c7291b70cb86256a7fc4ecb1b1","tid":1683400,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"求大家三罷"},{"pid":"2890c376772d34bbe8659aee5b12409765a92262","tid":1683400,"uid":333374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"一個星期罷一次有冇得諗"},{"pid":"58b5813b251ac662f7a6a47df3437e9eea1f50d2","tid":1683400,"uid":90073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28f716feefae3a2c5415a9813da09f14dd805654","tid":1683400,"uid":258748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:23:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab0d7f398b47254e0d5eeff93b85eed3f33b47c","tid":1683400,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7d2e7369f852f2e13cb9692c5aef8beb2465f1","tid":1683400,"uid":29292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2890c376772d34bbe8659aee5b12409765a92262","tid":1683400,"uid":333374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"一個星期罷一次有冇得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"不如唔好撚罷啦咁"},{"pid":"4e6e3b4d82e285240e307694a9b9ed1428e6bcee","tid":1683400,"uid":35364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"由八月開始呼籲建立工會，<br />\n無工會組織，無可能搞得成。<br />\n記得有人實牙實齒話搞工會，<br />\n唔知今時今日搞成點呢？"},{"pid":"7e8e3a7a10050ff3abcc88989ba40970ee5bf267","tid":1683400,"uid":296650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2890c376772d34bbe8659aee5b12409765a92262","tid":1683400,"uid":333374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"一個星期罷一次有冇得諗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"唔贊成 因為實際影響唔大 <br />\n一個禮拜一次 去到最後都會適應到<br />\n相反一次停一個禮拜 個影響係不可估量"},{"pid":"8e314a2a287e1509712e1f3509d26f0edc7713aa","tid":1683400,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2f8807fc2cb8c4a32752a7762b88e68672e2eb3","tid":1683400,"uid":296650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e6e3b4d82e285240e307694a9b9ed1428e6bcee","tid":1683400,"uid":35364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"由八月開始呼籲建立工會，<br />\n無工會組織，無可能搞得成。<br />\n記得有人實牙實齒話搞工會，<br />\n唔知今時今日搞成點呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得罷工唔應該由經濟行動起頭先 <br />\n相反應該由醫療 消防 呢啲民生方面開始 因為對社會影響力最大<br />\n而其他行業亦都要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">立即緊隨其後</span></span>開始罷工"},{"pid":"88fc17d7296ac75cb0e8677cf2e134a0b17dd138","tid":1683400,"uid":35557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"係就唔好罷得1日 <br />\n最起碼都1 個禮拜 乃至1個月"},{"pid":"68f28bc80d73e12af6379bef4f47ac6cad2c151c","tid":1683400,"uid":296650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88fc17d7296ac75cb0e8677cf2e134a0b17dd138","tid":1683400,"uid":35557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"係就唔好罷得1日 <br />\n最起碼都1 個禮拜 乃至1個月"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:40:04.000Z","msg":"YES<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f0a583ef40c1e7b1066f669c760edc785065c5","tid":1683400,"uid":280452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:42:58.000Z","msg":"咪下下整d無人會做既野自曝其短喇<br />\n又罷工又所謂死線升級<br />\n香港人大幅罷工既機會仲細過有人殺警<br />\n<br />\n香港人玩經濟圈就可能得"},{"pid":"d2dca9b68e90aeef2c3bc6b55ead4746e1fc061c","tid":1683400,"uid":197492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:46:13.000Z","msg":"push 民陣"},{"pid":"57df8433ff805fac4df790dea794ebb7a1c755df","tid":1683400,"uid":296650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25f0a583ef40c1e7b1066f669c760edc785065c5","tid":1683400,"uid":280452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:42:58.000Z","msg":"咪下下整d無人會做既野自曝其短喇<br />\n又罷工又所謂死線升級<br />\n香港人大幅罷工既機會仲細過有人殺警<br />\n<br />\n香港人玩經濟圈就可能得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:49:48.000Z","msg":"唉 我都知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但時日不多 照而家嘅進度行落去 我哋會變劣勢㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經濟圈固之然好 但係要有實際大影響仲需要一段時間 <br />\n而且而家人權法卡關 我哋去做啲大行動 可以有助推動<br />\n六 七月嗰陣時 啲人夠覺得火魔法冇可能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都冇人估到85罷工咁成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人 相信自己啦"},{"pid":"4c3f7d6d3dc19d6e7a78a00030